@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<h1 class="display-4 text-center">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
<div class="container mt-5">
    <p>At Event Registration System, your privacy is a top priority. This privacy policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect the personal information you provide when using our platform.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>When you interact with our Event Registration System, we collect the following information to provide the best service:</p>
    <ul class="list-unstyled">
        <li><strong>Personal Identification Information:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, and event details when you register for an event.</li>
        <li><strong>Transactional Data:</strong> Registration history, payment information, and event participation details.</li>
        <li><strong>Technical Information:</strong> IP address, browser type, device type, and access times, which help us improve user experience and system performance.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>Your information is used for the following purposes:</p>
    <ul class="list-unstyled">
        <li>To manage your registrations and provide customer support.</li>
        <li>To process transactions related to event registrations.</li>
        <li>To improve our platform’s functionality and user experience.</li>
        <li>To send you updates, notifications, and promotional offers related to our events (with your consent).</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-4">3. Data Protection and Security</h2>
    <p>We implement strong security measures to safeguard your personal information. All sensitive data is encrypted, and we use industry-standard security protocols to prevent unauthorized access, disclosure, or misuse of your information.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-4">4. Sharing Your Information</h2>
    <p>We do not sell or share your personal information with third parties for their own marketing purposes. However, we may share your data with trusted partners who assist us in operating our platform, provided they agree to protect your information in accordance with our standards.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-4">5. Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You have the right to access, update, or delete your personal information. If you wish to exercise these rights, please contact our support team.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-4">6. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this privacy policy periodically to reflect changes in our practices or the law. We will notify you of any significant changes by updating the date of this document.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-4">7. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions or concerns about your privacy or this policy, please reach out to us at <a href="mailto:support@eventregistrationsystem.com">support@eventregistrationsystem.com</a>.</p>

    <p class="text-muted mt-5">Last Updated: October 8, 2024</p>
</div>
